					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">blargg wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Well, that costs you quite a few cycles. I was also wondering why you used bit 1 of lfoPhase rather than bit 0. It seems that this merely halves the speed.</div>
<br />
<br />Because the phase has four states: %00 = up, %11 = down, %10 = down, %01 = up to give you the necessary cycle shape:
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">/\<br />----------- center frequency<br />&nbsp; \/<br /></div></div>

